                     <interp inst="t18290716-18-off93" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290716-18-off93" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290716-18-cd94" type="crimeDate">4th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290716-18-off93 t18290716-18-cd94"></join>, 2 sheets, value 7s.; 1 pillow-case, value 1s.; 3 shirts, value 10s.; 1 pair of stockings, value 6d.; 1 pair of drawers, value 1s.; 3 aprons, value 1s. 6d.; 2 handkerchiefs, value 1s., and 1 towel, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
